caption:
We’re proud to announce the launch of our ‘Sports for Change’ initiative in collaboration with Sportz Village Foundation. With mentorship, training, and infrastructure development opportunities in sports, this program aims to support and empower underprivileged students in 20 government schools across Delhi NCR. 

At Casio, our creed is creativity and contribution, and the ‘Sports for Change’ initiative is a testament to this belief.  By focusing on physical and mental well-being, fostering sportsmanship, and creating high-performance centers, we’re committed to nurturing young talent and driving social impact.

Together, we’re building a future where every child has the opportunity to excel in sports! 

#CasioIndia #SportsForChange #SocialImpact #YouthDevelopment
